meta.long_description: A community fork of KeePassX, which is itself a port of KeePass Password Safe. The goal is to extend and improve KeePassX with new features and bugfixes to provide a feature-rich, fully cross-platform and modern open-source password manager. Accessible via native cross-platform GUI and via CLI. Includes optional http-interface to allow browser-integration with plugins like PassIFox (https://github.com/pfn/passifox).
